items.name: Count People in Room
items.description: Count people in room by rotating and scanning with camera

items.name: Pick Up Object
items.description: Given an object name, detect and pick up the object using vision, base, arm, and gripper

items.name: Place the gripped object on a desk
items.description: Assume there is an object in the gripper, place the object on the top surface of the desk using vision, base, arm, and gripper

items.name: Pull Object
items.description: Given an object name, look for the object and use the gripper to grab on it and pull backward
